log5
=====================

Output logs

https://github.com/hailiang-wang/python-log5

Usage::

    import log5

    logger = log5.get_logger(log5.LN(__name__), output_mode=3)
    logger.debug('bar')
    logger.info('foo')


output_mode:

* 1: append to log file

* 2: print to stdout

* 3: both file and stdout

